<div class="mx-auto py-10">
  <div class="max-w-xl text-center mx-auto mb-12 text-gray-700">
    <p class="mb-4">Hello! I'm Jankees, the maker of RSSMailer.</p>

    <%= image_tag "jankees.jpg", class: "mb-12" %>

    <p class="mb-4">
      Today, I'm proud to introduce a new plan called <strong>RSSMailer Pro</strong> for people who
      follow more than 3 feeds.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      It lets you follow <strong>unlimited feeds, set custom delivery times, remove ads</strong>
      and more features will be added in the future! As a thank you for joining early, you can use
      the
      <span class="bg-yellow-200 py-1 px-2 rounded-lg">coupon "early-adopter"</span>
      to get a <strong>30% discount (life time)</strong>.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 font-bold">
      If you follow less than 3 feeds, you are welcome to stay on the free
      plan ‚Äì<br> you won't be affected at all.
    </p>

    <% classes = "mt-2 mb-8 btn btn--primary rounded-lg" %>
    <% unless current_user&.is_pro %>
      <% if current_user.present? %>
        <a href="#" data-theme="none" class="paddle_button <%= classes %>" data-product="570984" data-success="/thank-you/" data-passthrough="<%= current_user.id %>" data-coupon="<%= current_user.coupon %>" data-email="<%= current_user.email %>">
          <%= "Upgrade to RSSMailer PRO ‚ù§Ô∏è" %>Ô∏è</a>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to "Sign in, and upgrade to RSSMailer PRO ‚ù§Ô∏è", new_user_session_path, class: classes %>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
    <p class="mb-4">
      I'm also adding this option to make RSSMailer into a
      <%= link_to "sustainable business", open_path %>.
      This means that you'll be able to count on the service continuing and improving in the future.
    </p>

    If you have questions, please <a href="mailto:support@jankeesvw.com">let me know</a>.
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center mb-24">
    <div class="flex-grow border p-8 py-6 rounded bg-white shadow-sm m-3 h-auto max-w-xs">
      <header class="text-center">
        <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl">FREE</h1>
      </header>

      <hr class="border-t my-4">

      <ul class="leading-loose mb-10 features">
        <%= render "feature", feature: "Follow RSS feeds" %>
        <%= render "feature", feature: "Follow YouTube channels" %>
        <%= render "feature", feature: "Follow public Instagram feeds" %>
        <%= render "feature", feature: "3 feeds limit" %>
        <%= render "feature", feature: "Daily email" %>
        <%= render "feature", feature: "Occasional ads" %>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-grow border p-8 py-6 rounded shadow-lg m-3 bg-white max-w-sm">
      <header class="text-center">
        <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl">PRO</h1>
        <% if current_user.present? && current_user.discounted_monthly_price.present? %>
          <small class="text-sm font-bold">
            <span class="line-through">9.99$ per month</span><br>
            <span><%= current_user.discounted_monthly_price %>$ per month</span>
          </small>
        <% else %>
          <small class="text-sm font-bold">9.99$ per month</small>
        <% end %>

      </header>

      <hr class="border-t my-4">

      <ul class="leading-loose mb-10 features">
        <li class="mb-4 text-center text-gray-700">Everything from free and:</li>
        <%= render "feature", feature: "Unlimited feeds" %>
        <%= render "feature", feature: "Unlimited items per feed" %>
        <%= render "feature", feature: "100% ad free" %>
        <%= render "feature", feature: "Set a custom delivery time" %>
        <%= render "feature", feature: "Priority in queue", hint: "Sending all the emails can take upto a few hours, depending on the time of day. Emails of pro plan accounts are always sent before the free ones." %>
        <%= render "feature", feature: "Filter by keywords", soon: true %>
        <%= render "feature", feature: "Get email per feed (optional)", soon: true %>
      </ul>

      <div class="text-center">
        <% if current_user.present? && !current_user.is_pro? %>
          <a href="#" data-theme="none" class="paddle_button btn btn--primary rounded-lg" data-product="570984" data-success="/thank-you/" data-passthrough="<%= current_user.id %>" data-coupon="<%= current_user.coupon %>" data-email="<%= current_user.email %>">
            Upgrade to pro üëå</a>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.paddle.com/paddle/paddle.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
  Paddle.Setup({vendor: 102025});
</script>
